@dailyProductionId = <pega_el_id_de_produccion>
@customerId = <pega_el_id_del_cliente>
@deliveryId = <pega_el_id_del_repartidor>
@menuTypeId = <pega_el_id_del_tipo_de_menu>
@extraProductId = <pega_el_id_del_extra>
@lineId = <pega_el_id_de_la_linea>
@extraId = <pega_el_id_del_extra_de_produccion>

### ─────────────────────────────
### DAILY PRODUCTIONS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear producción — tipo PENDING (no se sabe aún cómo se entrega)
### fulfillment_type omitido o "PENDING" → sin delivery_id
### lines es opcional; si se omite, cargar cantidades después con PUT .../lines
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "production_date": "2026-06-15",
  "customer_id": "7039523b-9e7b-4da6-abab-9cb1204a094e",
  "fulfillment_type": "PENDING",
  "notes": null,
  "lines": [
    { "menu_type_id": "a6d7a71d-5da6-4515-8272-f98b0dc18f2f", "quantity": 4 }
  ]
}

###

### Crear producción — tipo DELIVERY (con repartidor desde el inicio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "production_date": "2026-06-16",
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "fulfillment_type": "DELIVERY",
  "delivery_id": "{{deliveryId}}",
  "notes": "Sin sal",
  "lines": [
    { "menu_type_id": "{{menuTypeId}}", "quantity": 8 }
  ]
}

###

### Crear producción — tipo PICKUP (retiro en sucursal, sin delivery_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "production_date": "2026-06-16",
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "fulfillment_type": "PICKUP",
  "notes": "",
  "lines": [
    { "menu_type_id": "{{menuTypeId}}", "quantity": 5 }
  ]
}

###

### Listar producciones del día
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar producciones del día — filtrar por estado de entrega
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15&fulfillment_type=DELIVERY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar producciones del día — filtrar por tipo de menú
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15&menu_type_id={{menuTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar producciones del día — filtrar por repartidor
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15&delivery_id={{deliveryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar producciones del día — buscar por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15&q=cliente
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar producciones del día — ordenar por mayor cantidad pedida
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15&sort=quantity&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar producciones del día — ordenar por menor cantidad pedida
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-15&sort=quantity&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener producción por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/one?dailyProductionId={{dailyProductionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar producción — asignar delivery a un PENDING
### Solo los campos enviados con valor no vacío se actualizan
PUT {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{dailyProductionId}}",
  "fulfillment_type": "DELIVERY",
  "delivery_id": "{{deliveryId}}"
}

###

### Actualizar producción — cambiar a PICKUP (limpia delivery_id automáticamente)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{dailyProductionId}}",
  "fulfillment_type": "PICKUP"
}

###

### Actualizar solo notas (sin tocar fulfillment_type ni delivery)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{dailyProductionId}}",
  "notes": "Sin gluten"
}

###

### Eliminar producción completa (borra líneas y extras por cascade)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{dailyProductionId}}"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### LÍNEAS DE CANTIDADES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Registrar/actualizar cantidad por tipo de menú (STAFF)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/lines
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menu_type_id": "{{menuTypeId}}",
  "quantity": 8
}

###

### Eliminar línea
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/lines/{{lineId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### EXTRAS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Agregar extra a producción
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/extras
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "extra_product_id": "{{extraProductId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Eliminar extra
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/extras/{{extraId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### TOTALES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Totales de cocina del día (por tipo de menú)
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/totals/kitchen?date=2026-06-15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Totales de extras del día
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/totals/extras?date=2026-06-16
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
